						"state": "Collapse",
						"value": "0",
						"explanation": "- Roll vs. Will to do anything besides talk or rest; failure causes unconsciousness\n- Each FP you lose below 0 also causes 1 HP of injury\n- Move, Dodge and ST are halved (B426)",
